    "body": "Hi @grapevinegizmos - this should be possible using the following code (assuming `otherSigner` is an address):\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nlet factory = await ethers.getContractFactory(\"MyContract\", {\r\n  libraries: {\r\n    MyLibrary: libaddress\r\n  },\r\n  signer: await ethers.getSigner(otherSigner)\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\nGoing to close this for now. Feel free to reopen if that code didn't work for you!",
